{"tid":832540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個落地獄既對答","createTime":"2018-09-22T21:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T02:13:07.000Z","uid":55774,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5a2a059045a3278cc6d3567e465614d9d6ac99","tid":832540,"uid":55774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T21:10:03.000Z","msg":"話說中學果陣有個肥既女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鍾意其中一個男同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超唔鍾意佢<br />\n<br />\n有一次小息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傾計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一句車埋去 : 你去死啦 !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :好 我依家就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知小息完左 打左鐘一陣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都未番黎<br />\n因為之前已經有先例 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為感情問題 一個人上左學校天台<br />\n所以我地其他人都好擔心<br />\n係到諗 死啦 佢係咪真係跳左落去 ...<br />\n<br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 屌 都無'bomb'一聲 姐係未跳啦 !<br />\n我地全部笑到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23923b2d637bc21254edbd4438dccefd24260ee","tid":832540,"uid":132898,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T23:00:13.000Z","msg":"唉屌以為過咗暑假就會正常返啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔記得今日係星期日"},{"pid":"ac98c43f66c707fe02cefc00b0dbddae3c03e161","tid":832540,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"咁即係有冇跳"},{"pid":"df9d92e249b6fb8f8afe9cc128c2c502db7147b1","tid":832540,"uid":207059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑啊屌你老味.jpg"},{"pid":"cb4c3e4b9d137a526dbb5588ab05cb06ddd04933","tid":832540,"uid":58002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}